comments: Arcidiacono (CHI) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Hill (MIL) and absorbs the contact.
Connaughton (MIL) moves alongside LaVine's (CHI) body and legally contests his driving shot attempt.
Bledsoe (MIL) makes incidental contact with White (CHI) as he retrieves the loose ball.
Hill (MIL) makes marginal contact with Arcidiacono (CHI) after the pick and doesn't affect his FOM.
Connaughton (MIL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with LaVine (CHI) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Bledsoe (MIL) goes to and not through White (CHI) during his legal spin move at the end of his drive.
Arcidiacono (CHI) and Connaughton (MIL) briefly engage and separate off ball.
LaVine (CHI) makes contact to Matthews' (MIL) arm prior to making contact with the ball.
Arcidiacono (CHI) initiates the contact by hooking Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm at the start of his drive.
White (CHI) makes marginal contact with Bledsoe (MIL) and doesn't affect his FOM.
LaVine (CHI) grabs Bledsoe's (MIL) jersey and affects his SQBR at the start of his drive.
Matthews (MIL) makes marginal contact with Markkanen (CHI) at the start of his drive and doesn't affect his SQBR.
Matthews (MIL) makes clean contact to the ball during Markkanen's (CHI) pass attempt.
White (CHI) makes marginal contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) after the release and does not affect his jump shot attempt or ability to follow-through naturally.
Connaughton (MIL) makes marginal contact with Harrison (CHI) and does not affect his ability to get to the loose ball.
